OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FHe said the former PCC's office had
OL,7,Fborrowed #65m in 2019 to pay for
OL,8,Fequipment, but had made no repayments
OL,9,Fsince then.
OL,11,F"It's a huge problem and a huge error
OL,12,F- there's no denying that, there's no
OL,13,Fdoubting it... this is a fundamental
OL,14,Fhuman error we think. We now need to
OL,15,Fwork out not just what went wrong but
OL,16,Fhow we fix it."
OL,18,FThe force is now seeking financial
OL,19,Fsupport from the government.
