OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FChief Constable Lauren Poultney said
OL,7,Fshe felt "great disappointment" at the
OL,8,Fnews and "the impact this will have on
OL,9,Fthe financial stability of South
OL,10,FYorkshire Police".
OL,12,F'There will of course be challenges'
OL,14,FShe added that the force had savings
OL,15,Fand reserves which would mitigate the
OL,16,Fimpact of the problem, but "this is
OL,17,Fnot how we would seek to manage our
OL,18,Ffinances and it will, of course, have
OL,19,Fimpacts on the service we deliver".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/10
