OL,6,F"I have that assurance and feel
OL,7,Fconfident through working together and
OL,8,Fwith the support of the Home Office we
OL,9,Fwill be able to stabilise the budget
OL,10,Fand protect the services we offer,"
OL,11,Fshe said.
OL,13,F"That said, there will of course be
OL,14,Fchallenges ahead as we work through
OL,15,Fthis.
OL,17,F"I have informed the workforce of this
OL,18,Ferror this morning and will do all I
OL,19,Fcan to offer them appropriate
OL,20,Freassurance so they can continue to
OL,21,Ffocus on the task ahead."
