OL,6,FThe force said it would "do everything
OL,7,Fwe can" to protect services but it was
OL,8,F"too soon to say" if jobs would be
OL,9,Faffected.
OL,11,FMr Coppard said the error came to
OL,12,Flight after the responsibilities for
OL,13,Fbudget oversight transferred from the
OL,14,Fformer office of the police and crime
OL,15,Fcommissioner to the mayor's office in
OL,16,FMay.
OL,18,FFormer Police and Crime Commissioner
OL,19,FDr Alan Billings said he only found
OL,20,Fout about the issue after the mayor
OL,21,Fissued a press release.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/10
