OL,6,F"That took me a little bit by
OL,7,Fsurprise," he said.
OL,9,F"It's a big issue in that it's money
OL,10,Fthat's got to be found but it's not a
OL,11,Fbig deal. I don't know why we're
OL,12,Fmaking such a big thing of it.
OL,14,F"These things happen all the time.
OL,15,FWhen you make a budget you put in what
OL,16,Fyou know and then you have to estimate
OL,17,Fthe things you don't know but you know
OL,18,Fthey're going to come down the track.
