OL,3,CYears of accounting blunders leave
OL,4,Cpolice force with #65m blackhole
OL,6,FLast year South Yorkshire Police had a
OL,7,Fbudget of #326m, of which 74% came
OL,8,Ffrom the government. The rest was paid
OL,9,Ffor through council tax.
OL,11,FA Home Office spokesperson said the
OL,12,Fgovernment welcomed the independent
OL,13,Freview.
OL,15,FThey added: "The financial issues
OL,16,Finherited and identified by the South
OL,17,FYorkshire mayor and the combined
OL,18,Fauthority are deeply concerning, and
OL,19,Fdo not reflect the high standards we
OL,20,Fexpect.
